Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, isn't it about time you tell me your thoughts regarding all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the rather "convenient" interaction between Kira and the Japanese police during this incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the very least, I can conclude that Kira and the Japanese police are working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.14,0:01:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Working together"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.86,0:01:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that's true, then Kira is... {\alpha&HFF&}the second-generation L.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that's true, then Kira is... the second-generation L.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, {\alpha&HFF&}but I'm only around 7% certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but I'm only around 7% certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Lester, when investigating, once you've decided on something,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you must believe in it absolutely, and if you're wrong, then "sorry" should suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:04.64,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(361,330)}Justice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:18.82,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,"Recently, crime has decreased in Japan, because if you do something bad, your name will be put on the Internet, and you'll be killed by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.40,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what my dad says."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you give me your name, we can't file a record.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Have mercy! Anything but my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.24,0:02:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll expose all your names on the Internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:39.13,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,500)}Kira-sama, please kill me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:03:02.41,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to announce, here and now, that Kira is Justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:06.79,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\fscy0\t(0,500,\fscy100)\pos(353,431)}Kira's Realm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:15.54,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an undeniable fact that I've been appointed by Kira to be their spokesman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:19.30,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,There may be those who'll attempt to take my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:27.97,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm prepared to lay down my life in order to bring you the words of Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:26.76,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(367,388)\fad(500,500)}New Japanese Investigative Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kira's Realm"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a distasteful title...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this world turning into?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:33.90,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Investigating Kira is an inexcusable thing! I'll even go as far as saying that it's a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd really be better off if they killed this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:42.07,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,The police, members of the public, criminals... whoever's investigating Kira, report them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's time for the President's press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's happening? {\alpha&HFF&}They said it's going to be a "message to the world"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's happening? They said it's going to be a "message to the world"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you lot seem to do is watch TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the United States of America...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...hereby acknowledge Kira and will not oppose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Success!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even America is finally accepting Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}What the hell is he saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell is he saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they fear Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. President!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When was this decision made?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give us more details?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that Kira is Justice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"? I'm not saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's a fact that thanks to Kira's powers, war has ceased.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Organized crime, and not just in our own country, has also been obliterated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we openly oppose Kira, we will be killed. That much is certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, while we won't acknowledge them as justice, we'll no longer take any measures to try and catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the same thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just say that you acknowledge Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself this country's representative?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this... {\alpha&HFF&}this is America we're talking about... and that was a presidential statement!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:04:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this... this is America we're talking about... {\alpha&HFF&}and that was a presidential statement!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this... this is America we're talking about... and that was a presidential statement!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, can I be serious for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the sudden change?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you normally aren't serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really believe, from the depths of your heart, that Kira is evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Matsuda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest... {\alpha&HFF&}I just can't believe that they're completely evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest... I just can't believe that they're completely evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe that Kira is Justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I believe that Kira is fighting against evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also an undeniable fact that the world has become a better place for those who live honest lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, Matsuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all just build on the fear of being slaughtered. This isn't real peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! {\alpha&HFF&}I know that much, but... I also understand the feelings of those who proclaim Kira to be their savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I know that much, but... {\alpha&HFF&}I also understand the feelings of those who proclaim Kira to be their savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I know that much, but... I also understand the feelings of those who proclaim Kira to be their savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been in a weak position...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a cop! {\alpha&HFF&}I can't acknowledge Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a cop! I can't acknowledge Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, and I want to catch them, because it's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to be crazy doing this without even being able to fully oppose Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that is crazy, Matsuda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?! Even you, Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Kira must realize that what they're doing is evil; {\alpha&HFF&}yet, they've still decided to sacrifice themselves to change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Kira must realize that what they're doing is evil; yet, they've still decided to sacrifice themselves to change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the type of justice Kira has chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm assuming that's what Kira probably is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not our job to decide whether Kira is good or evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only have to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we catch Kira, then Kira is evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira takes control of the world, then Kira is Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, henceforth, things will accelerate and the world will rapidly turn toward Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will definitely become Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to us now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll have to disband. Thanks to that chicken of a president.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... he's not even a chicken. He's lower than a maggot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a joke. There's no way acknowledging Kira is the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:07:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello... {\alpha&HFF&}welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello... welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put the gun down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please lower your guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shedding blood here will only be a waste of our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he killed our colleagues!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't make me say this again and again; or objective is to capture Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing Mello now would achieve nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has this gone exactly as you expected it to so far, Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. {\alpha&HFF&}You must have heard it from Lidner... about what happened with the second-generation L.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You must have heard it from Lidner... {\alpha&HFF&}about what happened with the second-generation L.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You must have heard it from Lidner... about what happened with the second-generation L.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to everything you've done, I've been able to narrow down Kira quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a device for you to solve your puzzles with!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello, if you want to shoot me, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello! {\alpha&HFF&}If you shoot Near, we'll have no choice but to shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello! If you shoot Near, {\alpha&HFF&}we'll have no choice but to shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello! If you shoot Near, we'll have no choice but to shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you both die here, what will that achieve?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll only make Kira happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. {\alpha&HFF&}Near, I only came to get back that photo you have of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Near, I only came to get back that photo you have of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. {\alpha&HFF&}This is the only photo... there are no copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. This is the only photo... {\alpha&HFF&}there are no copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. This is the only photo... there are no copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've dealt with anyone who would have known your face, at Wammy's House and elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say this with 100% certainty, but you won't be killed with that notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you wanted, Mello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of cooperating with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... {\alpha&HFF&}it'd be annoying to leave here with only this photo to show for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... it'd be annoying to leave here with only this photo to show for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer's notebook... {\alpha&HFF&}it's a Shinigami's notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer's notebook... it's a Shinigami's notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who have the notebook can see the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is going to believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can Mello achieve by lying about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he was going to lie, he'd lie about something more meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, Shinigami exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The notebook I had was once in the possession of someone other than a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at least one of the rules written in there is fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's about as much as I can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which of us will catch Kira first...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a race, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're both heading toward the same goal. {\alpha&HFF&}I'll be there waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're both heading toward the same goal. I'll be there waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fake rule...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given what's already happened, things such as heart attacks and being able to manipulate people before their deaths must be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Burning or shredding the notebook"? {\alpha&HFF&}The notebooks still exist and there's no way to test that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Burning or shredding the notebook"? The notebooks still exist and there's no way to test that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fake rule must be the one that states you'll die unless you write a name in the notebook within 13 days of the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gevanni, get me L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, we caught Mello... but he got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I was able to question him a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you mean he didn't get away, {\alpha&HFF&}you "allowed him" to get away? Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you mean he didn't get away, you "allowed him" to get away? {\alpha&HFF&}Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you mean he didn't get away, you "allowed him" to get away? Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he really did get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, he mentioned that that notebook was bound to a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been able to verify the existence of such a being?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Shinigami do in fact exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you wouldn't believe me even if I told you, so I never said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of things I'd like to ask that Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna be asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What bothers me the most are the rules written in the notebook, and the fact that there may be a fake rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, {\alpha&HFF&}I'd like to hear your thoughts on this. If there was a fake rule, which would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, I'd like to hear your thoughts on this. {\alpha&HFF&}If there was a fake rule, which would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L, I'd like to hear your thoughts on this. If there was a fake rule, which would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the process of elimination, it would have to be the one that says you'll die if you don't write a name within 13 days of the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you think that after all... {\alpha&HFF&}so do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you think that after all... so do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami, were there any fake rules written in the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. There weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a Shinigami with you, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:14:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? I think I'm beginning to understand this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is there, and is telling the Shinigami to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This dude is amazing. He's spot on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there was a fake, and the Shinigami is lying, it doesn't mean anything, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it would make Light's detainment pointless as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not true that you need to continue to write in the notebook to stay alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then there's no meaning to the fact that he did nothing for 13 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-{\alpha&HFF&}That's different. There's no way Light-kun could be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's different. {\alpha&HFF&}There's no way Light-kun could be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's different. There's no way Light-kun could be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before he died, the Deputy Chief himself confirmed that Light-kun doesn't have a notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, how about we verify it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will write Mello's name in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then if I die 13 days after Mello, {\alpha&HFF&}Kira wins. I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then if I die 13 days after Mello, Kira wins. {\alpha&HFF&}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then if I die 13 days after Mello, Kira wins. I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}What? This is about winning and losing now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What? {\alpha&HFF&}This is about winning and losing now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What? This is about winning and losing now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Verifying the "13 days" rule can only be a positive thing for the Kira investigation. There are no negatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to lay down my life for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm the only one to reject this idea, what sort of impression will that give the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us a while. We'll need to review this proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like everyone to give me their honest opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We can't do this out of respect for human life"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy for me to say, but I was the one detained, and it'll sound suspicious coming from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange. Killing Mello would avenge the Deputy Chief, so if Near wants to do that, I'm inclined to let him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that no one here is Kira, and ultimately, killing people with the notebook is not something we should be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we should try to follow in the Deputy Chief's footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also against the idea of verifying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, there's no way we can go ahead with verifying the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought... {\alpha&HFF&}Lastly, let me ask you one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought... Lastly, let me ask you one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all of you at the Japanese Investigative Headquarters... {\alpha&HFF&}have you ever thought, even once, that your "second-generation" L might be Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all of you at the Japanese Investigative Headquarters... have you ever thought, even once, {\alpha&HFF&}that your "second-generation" L might be Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all of you at the Japanese Investigative Headquarters... have you ever thought, even once, that your "second-generation" L might be Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anyone there who, having heard the conversation up to this point, is willing to cooperate with my investigation in any way,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then ring the number I'm about to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to reach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun can't be Kira. {\alpha&HFF&}No, I don't even want to think that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun can't be Kira. No, {\alpha&HFF&}I don't even want to think that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun can't be Kira. No, I don't even want to think that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the "13 days" rule is fake, he's not completely above suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... {\alpha&HFF&}I've got no choice now but to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... I've got no choice now but to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}Is this some kind of joke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this some kind of joke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you decide when you compare tomorrow's events with the death list I'm about to read you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. President, first, I'd like to thank you deeply for your approval of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, that's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like you to bring a swift end to the actions of the SPK, the organization out to get Kira, by ordering their dissolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, I would like you to use the police force, CIA,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FBI, and any other secret organizations to determine the whereabouts of the SPK members.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you uncover them, I would like you to tell me immediately via a communication point that I'll specify later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. President, whether you live a long life or not, is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demegawa-san! Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you going to New York all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to crush an organization that dares to oppose Kira-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A live report!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The President dropped me a line under orders from Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I don't know what's going on, and I don't even care!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our viewing figures are going to go up by 100... no, 120%!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, everyone, the age of Kira is upon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The previous L suspected Light-kun too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I was to suggest the need to investigate him again, then if he really is Kira, I'll just be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"13 days" rule, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, {\alpha&HFF&}we've known each other for a long time now... I know what's worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, we've known each other for a long time now... {\alpha&HFF&}I know what's worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa, we've known each other for a long time now... I know what's worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to do what you believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never fully trusted L.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now I'm doing this because I want to work with you, not Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ide...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact Near without Light-kun finding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you do, I'll ensure that no one finds out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun... {\alpha&HFF&}you're not Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun... you're not Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible! Live on TV, Demegawa's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Demegawa, have finally tracked down the base of an evil organization that seeks to capture our God, Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And along with my brothers, we have them surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, they appear to be hiding in this building!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Witness the power of the people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of Justice!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Near comes running out, I'll write his name in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! Misa will give it her best!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... at this rate we really will get dragged out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this one of Mello's plans to destroy the SPK?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or does the SPK operate in such ways that allow even members of the public to track down their location?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... {\alpha&HFF&}how dare you lie to me so blatantly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... how dare you lie to me so blatantly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I win, Near.
